snippet.title: NHL 15 -- Official E3 Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Built to harness the power of next generation consoles NHL 15 brings you the sights, sounds and feel of real hockey action like never before. Experience it for yourself on September 9th, 2014 when NHL 15 is available for Xbox One and Xbox 360.

To learn more about Xbox, please visit www.Xbox.com
